        <h2 class="chapter-title">章节 1: 问候语</h2>

        <p data-sentence-id="s1">Hello! My name is Alex. What's your name?</p>
        <p data-sentence-id="s2">Hi Alex, nice to meet you. I'm Maria.</p>
        <p data-sentence-id="s3">Nice to meet you too, Maria. Where are you from?</p>
        <p data-sentence-id="s4">I'm from Brazil. And you?</p>
        <p data-sentence-id="s5">I'm from Canada. Welcome to our <span class="glossary-term" data-word="school">school</span>!</p>
        <p data-sentence-id="s6">Thank you! It's a very <span class="glossary-term" data-word="friendly">friendly</span> place.</p>
        <p data-sentence-id="s7">I need to go to the <span class="glossary-term" data-word="bank" data-context="finance">bank</span> to deposit some money.</p>
        <p data-sentence-id="s8">We had a picnic on the <span class="glossary-term" data-word="bank" data-context="river">bank</span> of the river.</p>
        <p data-sentence-id="s9">The construction site used a large <span class="glossary-term" data-word="crane" data-context="machine">crane</span> to lift materials.</p>
        <p data-sentence-id="s10">A <span class="glossary-term" data-word="crane" data-context="bird">crane</span> flew gracefully over the marsh.</p>
        <p data-sentence-id="s11">I hope you enjoy your time here.</p>
        <p data-sentence-id="s12">I'm sure I will. See you around!</p>
        <p data-sentence-id="s13">See you!</p>

        <h3>关键短语 (Key Phrases)</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Hello! / Hi! (你好！)</li>
            <li>What's your name? (你叫什么名字？)</li>
            <li>My name is... / I'm... (我叫...)</li>
            <li>Nice to meet you. (很高兴见到你。)</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
